title: Matters Of The Heart Sunshine Yellow Maxi Dress
description: When it comes to Matters Of The Heart, a woman really needs to be careful. We're not saying to lock it away in a glass box and only bring it out on special occasions, but the heart is a fragile thing (and surprisingly strong when it needs to be). So in the care and feeding of the heart, one needs to treat it to special things now and then, and when the heart has a sudden urge, a want or longing, we find it's best to give in and splurge. Like if your heart wants this maxi dress, for example (just saying). Elegant dress features a plunging V neck on a fitted, ruching bodice, adjustable criss cross spaghetti straps, mesh overlay, and double slit skirt with an invisible zipper closure in back. Model is wearing a small. • 100% Polyester • Hand Wash Cold • Lined • Imported

title: Savanna Chic Leopard Sequin Dress
description: Why not be chic when you’re out on the savanna? You might make the wildlife a little jealous, because everybody knows that animals secretly want to wear sequins too, but without opposable thumbs, their dreams will never come true. But other than that, and the safety hazards it might incur, you’d look like a goddess! Better yet, how about you just look Savanna Chic at home or on vacation? Super shiney dress features sequins in a leopard print, a plunging v-neckline and faux wrap bodice, long sleeves, ruching on left hem, and an asymmetrical skirt. Model is wearing a small. • Self: 100% Nylon, Lining: 91% Rayon 9% Spandex • Machine Wash Cold • Lined Front and Skirt • Imported

title: Secret Keeper Light Camel Sweater Dress
description: Shhhh...can you keep something on the down low? This Secret Keeper sweater dress is simply the best thing in your closet. Just look at how you glow in it! Maybe you shouldn’t keep it all to yourself, you should totally let me borrow it. Just saying.  Sweater dress features a shift silhouette, a turtleneck, long sleeves with dropped shoulders, and v-shaped center seams in front. One size fits most. • 55% Mink Cashmere 35% Acrylic 10% Viscose • Hand Wash Cold • Unlined • Imported
details: Size Chart   Fit:  true to size; oversized fit   Length:  hits above knee   Bust:  room for movement   Waist:  room for movement   Hips:  room for movement   Undergarments:  bra friendly   Fabric:  fabric contains some stretch

title: Shimmer Down Rose Gold Sequin Dress
description: Get ready to Shimmer Down in this undeniably hot sequin dress. Don’t be surprised if there is a trail of fire in your wake wherever you go. No worries, it’ll go out eventually. The drool from your onlookers ought to do the trick. Rose gold sequin dress features a halter neckline with two button and loop closures in back of neck, a plunging front keyhole, an invisible back zipper, bust darts, and front waist darts. Model is wearing a small. • 100% Polyester • Hand Wash Cold • Lined • Imported
details: Size Chart   Fit:  runs slightly small; fitted   Length:  hits at mid thigh   Bust:  fitted   Waist:  fitted   Hips:  fitted with some room   Undergarments:  suggest adhesive bra or petals; nude undergarments recommended   Fabric:  fabric contains no stretch

title: Dream Your Own Reality Pink Tropical Maxi Dress
description: Ok, so you can’t live right on the island of your dreams with Hottie Mcsteamy while sippin’ outta coconut shells all day. However, you can drift around looking beyond gorgeous while you Dream Your Own Reality in this jaw-dropping maxi. Isn’t wearing this beauty just like living in paradise? I thought you would agree. This brightly printed maxi dress features a faux wrap bodice forming a deep v-neckline with a modesty snap, half length kimono sleeves, an elastic waist with matching tie belt, and a thigh-high slit in front. Model is wearing a small. • 100% Polyester • Dry Clean Only • Unlined • Imported
details: Size Chart   Fit:  true to size   Length:  floor length   Bust:  room for movement   Waist:  fitted; elastic   Hips:  room for movement   Undergarments:  bra friendly; nude undergarments recommended   Fabric:  fabric contains no stretch

title: Wild Idea Sweater Dress In Trendy Leopard Brown
description: Just whose Wild Idea was this? Oh. Wait. It’s mine. Lol! Well, it sounded like a fabulous plan at the time. No matter, thanks to my stellar sense of fashion I will at least look beyond chic in this sweater dress, even if the events for this evening weren’t fully thought through. Looking this good will make up for it, I’m certain. Sweater dress features a turtleneck, long sleeves with dropped shoulders, and ribbed cuffs, hem and collar. Model is wearing a small. • 100% Acrylic • Hand Wash Cold • Unlined • Imported
